OL,7,FA Michigan jury has found a school
OL,8,Fshooter's mother guilty of involuntary
OL,9,Fmanslaughter in the deaths of four
OL,10,Fstudents in 2021, Ian Woods reports
OL,12,FThe mother of a 15-year-old boy who
OL,13,Fshot dead four students has become the
OL,14,Ffirst parent in the United States to
OL,15,Fbe held responsible for the actions of
OL,16,Fa child carrying out a mass shooting,
OL,17,Fand been convicted of involuntary
OL,18,Fmanslaughter.
