OL,7,F"I have zero help for my mental
OL,8,Fproblems and it's causing me to shoot
OL,9,Fup the... school," he wrote.
OL,11,FThe four guilty verdicts - one for
OL,12,Feach student slain at Oxford High
OL,13,FSchool - were returned after around 11
OL,14,Fhours of deliberations.
OL,16,FJennifer and James Crumbley were the
OL,17,Ffirst parents in the US to be charged
OL,18,Fin a mass school shooting committed by
OL,19,Ftheir child - the latter faces trial
OL,20,Fin March.
