OL,7,FThe school was so concerned about the
OL,8,Fboy that they advised that the
OL,9,FCrumbleys get their son into
OL,10,Fcounselling in the next 48 hours.
OL,12,FJust a few hours later, Ethan Crumbley
OL,13,Fpulled a handgun from his bag and shot
OL,14,F10 students and a teacher.
OL,16,FFour people were killed, while a
OL,17,Ffurther seven were wounded.
